Our mantra is to build super-humans. 

00:02:03.260 --> 00:02:09.380
So it could be giving a blind person sight, or helping an older person stand up with the aid of mechatronics.

00:02:09.630 --> 00:02:12.710
And that’s our goal. Our goal is to help
people 

00:02:13.020 --> 00:02:15.060
while making a real kick-arse  extreme sports product.

